{"tid":1542194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逆向思維 如果太子冇人死 對話圖都係作嘅 對政府有咩好處","createTime":"2019-09-04T18:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T21:12:49.000Z","uid":199523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59796a21b43ec9d081f7a81557f84c06debf0247","tid":1542194,"uid":199523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:53:26.000Z","msg":"今日起見到多咗幾張新對話圖同記者會講1人失蹤<br />\n如果政府知冇人死 特登做假玩我地 對件事有咩好處 而家咁樣只會令我地更加想查明真相 如果係有人死 咁佢應該冷處理加shift focus (即係而家做緊嘅嘢 電視講撤回)<br />\n大家集思廣益下<br />\n利申 我信有死人 但啲圖講到阿豬阿狗都知內幕咁 要瞞呢個大核彈 會唔會咁疏忽 封站都封24個鐘 封人地個口唔識封? (當然唔排除醫護高風亮節啦)"},{"pid":"ea2962c7c1694b7d977ceb574e95c94c46e1b86d","tid":1542194,"uid":106252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"係咁做fake news出嚟 等啲人以為係假嘅 唔再去理個真相"},{"pid":"b599de18858749176db0d19a154c3cbe4db68ba9","tid":1542194,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">(真緊急)見字幫手copy廣傳 星期五1930集氣千人太子站獻花\n\n煲大個輿論\n\n生要見人 死要見屍</code></pre>"},{"pid":"43e4dcb8e3353395b7010f47270b09d7ff2109e5","tid":1542194,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aee785d9977eaae418036d3f9f2ab3e2ed9a0c2","tid":1542194,"uid":199523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea2962c7c1694b7d977ceb574e95c94c46e1b86d","tid":1542194,"uid":106252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"係咁做fake news出嚟 等啲人以為係假嘅 唔再去理個真相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:04:23.000Z","msg":"啱 好似都有道理 或者浪費時間令我地私下fact check都唔去迫佢拎cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772929da3f5e210aca8ad47903e378ce2995fb11","tid":1542194,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T19:05:15.000Z","msg":"俾對家屈我地除咗黃衣人之外無人死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class